reviews.review_text: I heard the Van Halen sample too!!!! There is no doubt a sample of Van Halen's "Running with the Devil" in the drums segment!!!!

Have You heard the" If I Only Had  A Brain" space ? I love Drums and Space 


It is a  Hendrix sample then VH    -The Hendrix sample is from Electric Lady Land

Random comments Man, I love these Cal Expo '92 shows more every time I play them.

This was the first time I ever attended three shows in a row, one of them being a miracle ticket. I

Garcia's voice sounds better with age to me.

where are the new songs?? Strange how they don't even do "So Many Roads" or "Corinna" at this run after flogging those selections on the spring tour.  A very solid run of shows with the last night being the hottest, imo.  Second night is strange and unfocused.  So weird to have Truckin early in the set and Saint going into drums like that.  As someone mentioned, the drums and space from this show are incredible.  The Hendrix sample or quote is from "1983" I think.  Gloria is the late afternoon on a hot summery day.
